Name: TacTac Prologue
About the game: Puzzle-adventure game where you adopt the rol of Dunai, a young guy from Gaab. He's soon moving to the big city but before doing so he'll have to say goodbye to his loved ones. On his way he'll have to solve a desapearing case. Explore the town of Gaab freely, you'll find all kind of colorful characters. Investigate the town to unveil the secrets that Gaab hides. Also the circus has arribed to town, go take a look at the attractions and the games it offers. With a unique and original artistic style you'll fall in love with the scenaries and characters of the game. The game counts with two cases to solve and more than 20 different puzzles on the way that will make you rack your brains and are distributed all over Gaab. Enjoy this prologue, this is just the beginning of a big story! This game can be played in English, Spanish or Catalan.
